to reach 100%.

29:09.225 --> 29:10.966
So, consider it done.

29:11.010 --> 29:12.228
Fill 'er up!

29:23.979 --> 29:25.589
Excuse me,
everyone.

29:25.633 --> 29:27.200
I know that this
is not my party,

29:27.243 --> 29:28.810
and you are all having
eco-friendly fun,

29:28.854 --> 29:29.811
so I'll make this quick.

29:29.855 --> 29:31.595
Some of you
probably remember

29:31.639 --> 29:32.901
the last time I was up here,

29:32.945 --> 29:34.381
to announce that

29:34.424 --> 29:35.730
I was taking some time
for myself.

29:35.774 --> 29:37.688
MAN: Blake Time!Exactly.

29:37.732 --> 29:39.342
And I am not gonna lie to you.

29:39.386 --> 29:41.823
Blake Time was a good time.

29:43.216 --> 29:44.521
But...

29:44.565 --> 29:46.828
all good things
must come to an end,

29:46.872 --> 29:48.830
to make room for better things.

29:48.874 --> 29:51.702
Indeed, you may have heard that
I have found a new passion.

29:51.746 --> 29:54.009
I am the owner

29:54.053 --> 29:56.620
of Atlanta's newest
professional soccer team.

29:58.492 --> 30:00.711
But that is not the
most exciting thing

30:00.755 --> 30:02.365
on the horizon.

30:02.409 --> 30:04.150
I'm expanding.

30:04.193 --> 30:05.934
Because my fiancée
Cristal and I

30:05.978 --> 30:08.545
are expecting a new baby.

30:10.852 --> 30:12.332
A new what?

30:12.375 --> 30:14.160
I think he said a new baby.

30:14.203 --> 30:15.726
BLAKE:
So I would like to propose

30:15.770 --> 30:17.032
a toast

30:17.076 --> 30:18.077
to me time

30:18.120 --> 30:20.035
becoming we time...

30:21.515 --> 30:22.995
...becoming three time.

30:24.518 --> 30:25.562
Stay green, people.

30:32.918 --> 30:36.095
This is going to be
an amazing adventure.

30:43.929 --> 30:45.539
Hey.

30:45.582 --> 30:47.062
I've been looking for you.

30:47.106 --> 30:48.324
For someone who almost died,

30:48.368 --> 30:50.370
you really are up and about.

30:50.413 --> 30:51.675
Well, I didn't almost die.

30:51.719 --> 30:52.851
I was dead.

30:52.894 --> 30:54.069
Which is why I'm still
at half-speed.

30:54.113 --> 30:55.418
But I'd like to think

30:55.462 --> 30:56.898
that's better than most
people's full-speed.

30:58.030 --> 30:59.422
Hey, have you seen Culhane?

30:59.466 --> 31:00.989
No.

31:01.033 --> 31:03.905
But, um, I want
to talk to you about that.

31:03.949 --> 31:05.951
Look, I care
about you, Fallon.

31:05.994 --> 31:07.517
And if you're really gonna
marry this dude,

31:07.561 --> 31:09.302
I need to make sure he told you
everything that went down.

31:09.345 --> 31:11.913
Hey, I'm not happy
about what happened,

31:11.957 --> 31:13.219
but he explained it to me.

31:13.262 --> 31:14.611
And it sounded like he did
what he had to do.

31:14.655 --> 31:16.787
So he told you
that he kept working for Ada

31:16.831 --> 31:18.267
even after he got
the blackmail back?

31:18.311 --> 31:20.052
That he chose to stay?

31:20.095 --> 31:22.228
Excuse me?I'm just trying
to look out for you.

31:22.271 --> 31:24.491
Maybe you need
to talk to your fiancé.

31:30.714 --> 31:33.456
What are you hiding out
from down here?

31:33.500 --> 31:35.458
Take your pick.

31:35.502 --> 31:37.025
You were right.

31:37.069 --> 31:38.374
Well, you're gonna have to be
more specific.

31:38.418 --> 31:39.723
I'm right about
a lot of things.

31:39.767 --> 31:42.378
Culhane lied to me. Again.

31:42.422 --> 31:44.598
And now I can forgive him

31:44.641 --> 31:46.948
and save him by putting
my own life in jeopardy,

31:46.992 --> 31:49.559
or I can do nothing

31:49.603 --> 31:52.084
and let him pay for
what he did with Ada.

31:53.433 --> 31:54.956
I'm just not sure
which fate he deserves.

31:55.000 --> 31:56.653
