you're going to tell me anyway?

34:16.793 --> 34:18.317
Well, it means
someone bought it.

34:18.360 --> 34:19.448
Shows what you know.

34:19.492 --> 34:22.886
Well, congratulations.Thank you.

34:22.930 --> 34:26.803
Have you seen Fallon?

34:26.847 --> 34:29.719
