bought that thing.Well, it's for a good cause.

34:29.763 --> 34:31.286
Besides,
I thought it was charitable

34:31.330 --> 34:33.723
to get this... thing

34:33.767 --> 34:36.900
out of circulation.

34:36.944 --> 34:38.380
So, have you...

34:38.424 --> 34:40.382
heard any more
about Steven?

34:42.819 --> 34:45.822
No. Nothing.

34:45.866 --> 34:47.389
Well, if you do
get to talk to him,

34:47.433 --> 34:48.999
just tell him that I...

34:50.523 --> 34:53.221
...just tell him
that I hope he's doing okay.

35:04.014 --> 35:06.060
I don't understand why you
were afraid to tell me.

35:08.323 --> 35:10.760
With all that's been going on
with your other children...

35:12.153 --> 35:13.328
...I was worried
it wasn't a good time

35:13.372 --> 35:14.503
to talk about a new one.

35:14.547 --> 35:16.505
And now with the soccer team

35:16.549 --> 35:19.726
and all these travel plans...

35:22.337 --> 35:24.600
I don't know
if you're aware of this,

35:24.644 --> 35:27.473
but I happen to be
a billionaire.

35:27.516 --> 35:30.824
Which means wherever we go,
we can take our baby with us.

35:30.867 --> 35:33.174
Are you sure?

35:33.218 --> 35:35.133
Yeah.

35:35.176 --> 35:37.178
I wasn't a very good father
the first time around.

35:37.222 --> 35:40.616
I was busy with work
and trying to prove myself to...

35:40.660 --> 35:42.488
well, everyone.

35:42.531 --> 35:44.185
This is a chance

35:44.229 --> 35:47.014
for me to do it again
the right way.

35:48.581 --> 35:51.061
You've given me a gift,
Cristal.

35:51.105 --> 35:53.107
Thank you.

36:36.846 --> 36:38.370
It's taken care of.

36:38.413 --> 36:40.937
What? I mean, how did...

36:40.981 --> 36:42.852
You know what, never mind.

36:42.896 --> 36:44.637
I'm just relieved.

36:44.680 --> 36:47.466
Y-You're sure?Yes.

36:47.509 --> 36:50.425
Nico has plenty to say that
doesn't include Michael Culhane.

36:56.301 --> 36:59.913
Okay. I know
this has been rough,

36:59.956 --> 37:02.132
but I'm glad
you finally realized the truth.

37:02.176 --> 37:05.614
Nothing like this
will ever happen again.

37:05.658 --> 37:08.400
I know it won't.

37:08.443 --> 37:10.880
Because this is over.

37:12.317 --> 37:14.580
The wedding is off.

37:14.623 --> 37:17.235
You lied to me, Michael.

37:17.278 --> 37:19.237
I know you kept working for Ada.

37:19.280 --> 37:21.761
And I know you kept
misleading me.

37:21.804 --> 37:23.763
And I might be able to
forgive you someday,

37:23.806 --> 37:26.592
but I'll never be able
to trust you again.

37:28.289 --> 37:30.248
I just won't.

37:30.291 --> 37:32.250
Fallon.

37:45.437 --> 37:47.395
What's up, Mom?

37:47.439 --> 37:50.180
Whoa, whoa, whoa, wait, no.
Slow-slow down.

37:50.224 --> 37:53.140
What-what are you talking about,
robbed? What happened?

37:53.183 --> 37:56.230
Okay. A-Are you guys all right?

37:56.274 --> 37:58.188
Okay, okay.
Just don't-don't do anything.

37:58.232 --> 38:00.234
I'll be right there.

38:03.193 --> 38:06.196
Are you feeling okay?

38:08.286 --> 38:10.723
I'm feeling pretty good,
actually.

38:10.766 --> 38:13.726
I'm glad I went tonight.

38:13.769 --> 38:16.337
You didn't make up
with Culhane, did you?

38:16.381 --> 38:19.340
Not exactly.

38:19.384 --> 38:23.649
But I think we're even,
and I'm gonna let it go.

38:23.692 --> 38:27.870
I was dead, Monica.
That changes you.

38:27.914 --> 38:31.657
Everything looks
a little different now.

38:31.700 --> 38:34.877
Your perspective changes.

38:34.921 --> 38:36.488
I don't know if it's gonna last,

38:36.531 --> 38:38.751
but I know
there's one more thing

38:38.794 --> 38:41.449
I have to do
while I feel this way.

38:41.493 --> 38:43.495
And you're not gonna like it.

38:43.538 --> 38:45.192
What is it?

38:45.235 --> 38:46.541
♪ You really got a hold on me

38:46.585 --> 38:48.238
Hand me my phone, will you?

38:48.282 --> 38:51.372
♪ You really got a hold on me♪♪ Baby

38:51.416 --> 38:54.897
