39:11.914 --> 39:14.874
I never had a chance
to say bye to you.

39:14.917 --> 39:17.398
But now I don't want to.

39:17.442 --> 39:18.921
I want to start over.

39:18.965 --> 39:20.619
So call me.

39:20.662 --> 39:22.316
Please.

39:22.360 --> 39:24.666
Look...

39:24.710 --> 39:28.801
I know you feel changed
or whatever.

39:28.844 --> 39:31.934
But she hasn't.

39:31.978 --> 39:35.634
All she's gonna do is come here,
let us down again,

39:35.677 --> 39:37.636
