Hey. It's me.

40:00.441 --> 40:03.313
Steven. Hi there.

40:03.357 --> 40:04.532
"Hi there"?

40:04.576 --> 40:06.404
That's all you have
to say to me?

40:06.447 --> 40:07.927
Why are you even calling?
I should be talking

40:07.970 --> 40:11.321
