40:11.365 --> 40:13.106
Wait, wait, wait.

40:13.149 --> 40:15.064
Sam, I'm so sorry.

40:15.108 --> 40:17.632
You need to forget
you ever saw those papers.

40:17.676 --> 40:19.765
Just pretend
they never even happened.What?

40:19.808 --> 40:22.071
I don't want a divorce.

40:22.115 --> 40:24.509
I never did. It...

40:24.552 --> 40:26.859
it was the ayahuasca.

40:26.902 --> 40:29.427
I-I have no idea
why it affected me like that,

40:29.470 --> 40:32.473
but I got a little crazy
for a few days, and...

40:32.517 --> 40:35.694
I'm back to normal now.
I'm-I'm so sorry.

40:35.737 --> 40:37.609
Does this mean
you're coming home now?

40:37.652 --> 40:40.438
Soon, yeah. Yeah.

40:40.481 --> 40:43.005
I just have a few more things
I need to take care of here.

40:43.049 --> 40:44.833
Well, why don't I
come visit you.

40:44.877 --> 40:46.531
I know I didn't love Paraguay,

40:46.574 --> 40:49.882
but I hate being apart
even more.

40:49.925 --> 40:53.320
Okay. I'll, uh, I'll call you
this weekend to make plans.

40:53.363 --> 40:56.584
All right?
I-I've got to run for now.

40:56.628 --> 40:58.020
I love you, Sam.

40:58.064 --> 40:59.239
♪ Hold me

